碟名都定咗《亂世佳人》，但Leslie唔明，所以拗咗好耐，佢話自己狀態唔好，要畀多啲時間佢，最後都錄到十隻歌（最尾一隻歌《玻璃之情》），隻碟佢屋企人一直唔想佢出，最後出動咗法庭禁制令，仲謠言話啲歌係夾硬發死人財。<br />\n張國榮過身之前，我兩個幾月冇見過佢，隻碟錄咗成三個幾月，我記得佢打電話畀我，當時我喺法國，喺巴黎一條街歎緊咖啡，當時天氣好凍，但有陽光，佢話：「喂，小寶，我係Leslie」，我話「係咪真㗎，你唔好玩我啦，把聲咁嘅」，佢話「我真係好病，隻碟我錄晒，我錄得好辛苦，你唔好聽人哋嘅閒言閒語，你亦要相信我冇因為呢啲嘢影響我哋之間嘅感情，我哋係好朋友。」"},{"pid":"dda2baa5f808620d82dfe4a7313c2a96471927c6","tid":765387,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df22fe69addb8f582439eb3644a3cea4db8e017","tid":765387,"uid":165244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"偷情個live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec46aa58c99b4b28fb7b22eca8ff14aa286d2c3","tid":765387,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"親愛的哥哥,凱彤:<br />\n<br />\n如果你太累 及時地就道別沒有罪<br />\n<br />\n有心人 上<br />\n<br />\n07/08/2018"},{"pid":"328ce9c0d5c6808d255bc27acc0d6bf2c9158ffb","tid":765387,"uid":203615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"Miss you much,Leslie"}]}